        <sponsor name-id="S253">Mr. Durbin</sponsor> (for himself and <cosponsor name-id="S339">Mr. Kirk</cosponsor>) introduced the following bill; which was read twice and referred to the <committee-name committee-id="SSGA00">Committee on Homeland Security and Governmental Affairs</committee-name>
